## EL表达式常用输出形式

#### Book类

```java
/**
 * @author 云禄
 * @version 1.0
 */

public class Book {
    private String name;//书名
    private String[] writer;//作者
    private List<String> reader;//读者
    private Map<String , String> topics;//话题

    @Override
    public String toString() {
        return "Book{" +
                "name='" + name + '\'' +
                ", writer=" + Arrays.toString(writer) +
                ", reader=" + reader +
                ", topics=" + topics +
                '}';
    }

    public String getName() {
        return name;
    }

    public void setName(String name) {
        this.name = name;
    }

    public String[] getWriter() {
        return writer;
    }

    public void setWriter(String[] writer) {
        this.writer = writer;
    }

    public List<String> getReader() {
        return reader;
    }

    public void setReader(List<String> reader) {
        this.reader = reader;
    }

    public Map<String, String> getTopics() {
        return topics;
    }

    public void setTopics(Map<String, String> topics) {
        this.topics = topics;
    }
}
```

#### JSP页面

```jsp
<%@ page import="com.felix.bean.Book" %>
<%@ page import="java.util.ArrayList" %>
<%@ page import="java.util.HashMap" %><%--
  Created by IntelliJ IDEA.
  User: a728910
  Date: 2026/3/29
  Time: 13:46
  To change this template use File | Settings | File Templates.
--%>
<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" language="java" isELIgnored="false" %>
<html>
<head>
    <title>el 表达式输出数据</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>el 表达式输出数据</h1>
<%
    //常见 Book 对象，放入相关的属性
    Book book = new Book();
    book.setName("假如给我三天光明");
    book.setWriter(new String[]{"Felix , Tom , Jack"});
    ArrayList<String> readers = new ArrayList<>();
    readers.add("Alias");
    readers.add("jar");
    book.setReader(readers);
    HashMap<String, String> topics = new HashMap<String, String>();
    topics.put("topics1" , "Good");
    topics.put("topics2" , "awful");
    book.setTopics(topics);

    //把 book 放入 request 域对象
    request.setAttribute("book" , book);
%>
  
book对象: ${book}<br/>
book.name: ${book.name}<br/>
book.writer: ${book.writer}<br/>
book.writer[0]: ${book.writer[0]}<br/>
book.readers: ${book.reader}<br/>
book.reader(第2个): ${book.reader.get(1)}<br/>
book.topics(第一个): ${book.topics.get("topics1")}


</body>
</html>
```

